data.title: Valve Corporation
data.meta_description: Valve Corporation, (formerly Valve Software, commonly known as Valve) is an American video game development and digital distribution company, as well as the creator of Dota 2.
data.text:
Liquipedia Dota 2 needs more help, are you able to? You just have to register an account and then log in to edit our pages. If you have any questions you can join the #dota2 channel on Discord.

Our friends over at Dota 2 Wiki (Fandom) are moving in with us! Check out the brand new Dota 2 game content here. If youd like to help out, join our Discord.
